有些红肿。另外，在李子柒的手臂上，也能看出来出现明显的过敏症状。李子柒讲述学漆艺过敏细节：割漆回家脸肿成电视机，整个团队去医院打抗敏针 | 极目新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-153c3e5b4e589ca1523df86142a29ece_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "34 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4052529179"}}, "attached_info": "CkEItJqW27eClpFSEAMaCTExMTc4NzEwNCD+rtG5BjAAOIcCQApyCjQwNTI1MjkxNzl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1731636994.414496", "card_id": "Q_4186936773", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 162}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "世预赛中国男足击败巴林，跃居小组第 4，积分追平澳大利亚沙特，国足还有望冲击附加赛吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "冲击附加赛有望？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-ae9447d9f6dffe685c3ec10195337952_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "32 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/4186936773"}}, "attached_info": "CkEItJqW27eClpFSEAMaCTExMTgxMzg4NyCev9i5BjAAONwBQAtyCjQxODY5MzY3NzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "12_1731636994.417545", "card_id": "Q_3300861668", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何在不降低清晰度的情况下减小视频的大小？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "录课视频太大了，超过 2G 不能上传，如何在不降低清晰度的情况下减小视频的大小？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-9e323b71b59e8d42891ab038887147da_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "30 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/3300861668"}}, "attached_info": "CkEItJqW27eClpFSEAMaCTExMTYzNjY1OCCOm6u5BjAAOPABQAxyCjMzMDA4NjE2Njh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed"